{
  "stem": "1733.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 233.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the little girl started crying, because she didn't realize that people are starved.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I bent down to pick up the-- to pick up the pot and to give it to her.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, an  SS came over, and I was the only one left there, because everybody ran away with the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he hit me in the left side of the temple with the butt of the-- of the rifle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I started bleeding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a scarf on that was full of lice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I put it into some muddy water, and I wrapped it on my head.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was-- that was the cure for me, without potatoes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we had no markings on the  uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nothing to identify us that we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just prisoners like everybody else in the same, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't have any other incident where I was pointed out being a Jew, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- we had yellow stars--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--on the uniform.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know that, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have-- we didn't have any markings on that transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, just thinking back now, we didn't have any.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't-- you couldn't distinguish between Jews and non-Jews on that transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't know whether we had-- everybody had yellow bands, but they were-- or there was a yellow mark on the back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I know that there was no distinguish marking between Jews and non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And talking about that transport, we came up again into this Czech village.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
